kde-service-menu-reimage (2.6) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Added support for KDE Plasma 6
  * Massive localization expansion: added support for Arabic, Esperanto, Spanish,
    Persian, French, Japanese, Polish, Portuguese, Russian, Turkish, and Chinese
  * Added "Social OG" (1200x630) resolution preset for easy social media sharing
  * Refactored notification logic: single summary notification for batch operations
  * Added "Create animated GIF from a set of images" feature
  * Added "Convert to Base64" feature integrated into the main script
  * Refactored binary detection with ImageMagick 7 (magick) support
  * Optimized script performance (reduced redundant localization calls)
  * Modernized .desktop icons for a premium Plasma 6 experience
  * Enhanced install.sh with real-time dependency checks
  * Fixed bug in run_timestamp using hardcoded test file
  * Modernized installation and uninstallation scripts
  * Updated copyright years to 2007-2026

 -- Giuseppe Benigno <giuseppe.benigno@gmail.com>  Sun, 26 Apr 2026 12:15:00 +0200

